modules.description: This module implements delimited continuation operators using the `Delimcc_of_fxhandler` abstraction, enabling manipulation of control flow through prompts and subcontinuations. It provides functions like `shift`, `control`, `reset`, and `abort` to capture, compose, and manipulate delimited continuations, working with prompt and subcont types. Concrete use cases include implementing backtracking, coroutines, and advanced control structures like exception handling or transactional execution.
